I found one broader reachable variant beyond the submitted wording: `route` also succeeds with an empty plugin list, so this is not just a Uniswap-plugin quirk. The core invariant is weaker than intended: the router only proves it did not lose `tokenOut`, not that any payment or delivery happened.
